,"url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1395,4719,26804,103938,134321],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"怎样才能让孩子成长为一个有主见的人？这是很多家长都希望达成而又不知该如何达成的心愿。 作为孩子的妈妈，我也是一样的心情。 现在我们身边的信息太多了，孩子们也一样，每天都要面对很多纷繁复杂的信息。 孩子的心智还没有成熟，要让他们独自分辨出有价值的信息真的很难； 正是因为信息量太大，孩子才容易被带偏，才不容易形成自己的主见。 我是在家里的时候努力做到以下几点： 1、当社会上出现一个热点话题时，和孩子一起讨论，倾听孩子的意见，不去辩论观点的对错。 2、例如选课或者是学校的活动，让孩子自己选择参加。 3、吃晚饭或者周末有空的时候，让孩子听央视等主流媒体的新闻报道，树立孩子正确的价值观。 这是我目前探索的方法，大家都有哪些更好的方法呢？"},"attached_info":"CkAIzaGuyO+e+q8/EAMaCTExMTAwODE2NiCGu5K4BjAAOKQCQBByCTc3ODExNDg4NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-d3d0f204bfe58659d975ad821fcbed2c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"17_1728714094.465975","card_id":"Q_818748479","target":{"id":818748479,"title":"大学生不合群奇怪吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/818748479","type":"question","created":1728640324,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":45,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1746,113884],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"室友平常喜欢在宿舍里打游戏聊天，就我一个人喜欢去图书馆 ，聚餐啥的我也比较少参加。我担心这会让我和室友的关系变得疏远。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IzaGuyO+e+q8/EAMaCTExMTA4MTI5NiDE6qO4BjAAOC1AEXIJODE4NzQ4NDc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-487b4e4c9a7c8fb419a9d43758dec776_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1728714094.466583","card_id":"Q_807463176","target":{"id":807463176,"title":"如果你是编剧，会如何设计《749 局》的剧情？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/807463176","type":"question","created":1728561278,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":54,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_tok